I was here on my trip to Da Nang and there's no arguing about the hotel's prime location close to the city center and right next to the beach. From the room, I could embrace the entire ocean. Not only that, the rooms here are very spacious and clean, and the breakfast is excellent. If you are a couple, you should try going to the hotel's top bar to have a cocktail and admire the sea, it's incredibly romantic. As for the hotel staff, they are exceptional. The staff is always cheerful and friendly, ready to assist, especially Rosy, who always answered my questions and provided me with great experiences in Da Nang with a smile always on her face. This is the best hotel and I will definitely come back. ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è
