T T wrote a review Nov 2023
spice spa @ alacarte
Type of massage : stretch (Thai massage) Therapist : Quynh Ngoc I received a massage on the last day of my trip to Da Nang. My body was quite tired due to Marble Mountain visit, but I found myself completely refreshed when I got the treatment done. Since it's a hotel spa, it's more expensive than massage parlors in town, but considering the fact that I received the treatment at a campaign price, the high level of technique, and the cleanliness, I was very satisfied with the experience.
